        <item>
            <title>议员指厨余回收设施不敷应用　公屋居民不懂用二维码开厨余回收桶</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/smart-food-waste-bin/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=smart-food-waste-bin</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/smart-food-waste-bin/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:17:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智能厨余回收桶]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229891</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>立法会议员陈凯欣表示，目前香港厨余回收设施严重不足，部分公屋智能厨余回收桶长期饱和，有机会引起衞生问题，因此建议当局加派人手协助居民。</p><p>立法会议员陈凯欣接受港台节目《千禧年代》采访时表示，早前她曾经到深水埗元州邨视察厨余回收情况，发现部分居民不懂得如何扫描二维码使用智能厨余回收桶，所以就直接将厨余弃置于回收桶旁边，或附近的垃圾桶，引起衞生问题。</p><p>陈凯欣认为，市民弃置厨余高峰期普遍属午餐及晚饭后，因此建议政府在高峰期加派人手从旁协助居民使用及加快清理厨余回收桶。陈凯欣另外又指，智能厨余回收桶不足应付需求，目前两幢公屋大厦共用一部智能厨余回收桶已有饱和情况，如附近大厦居民希望回收厨余，就无法使用公屋内的厨余回收桶。</p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1749235-20240417.htm">RTHK</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/smart-food-waste-bin/life-tech/smartcity/">议员指厨余回收设施不敷应用　公屋居民不懂用二维码开厨余回收桶</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/smart-food-waste-bin/life-tech/smartcity/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>全港戏院日开始售票，网民：「银行已扣钱但未收到确认电邮」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/cinema-day-2024/movie-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cinema-day-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/cinema-day-2024/movie-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:30:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影视娱乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[全港戏院日]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229900</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港戏院商会继去年后再度宣布举办「全港戏院日」，4 月 21 日当日全港 63 间戏院所有电影票价划一售 30 元。今日中午 12 时起各大戏院网站开始售票，小编刚刚（13:53）尝试到其中一间影院网站排队，留意到前面有逾 6,000 人排队，场面墟冚。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229902" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417135258-694x458.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417135258-694x458.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417135258.jpg 1277w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编刚刚尝试到其中一间影院网站排队，留意到前面有逾 6,000 人排队</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229927" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-3-391x580.jpg" alt="" width="391" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-3-391x580.jpg 391w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-3.jpg 607w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 391px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网友 12 时许尝试排队，前面有近 20000 人</p><p>LIHKG 讨论区有网民表示，在正式开售（12:00）前在戏院应用程式已经买到戏飞。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229928" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2-2-672x580.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2-2-672x580.jpg 672w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2-2.jpg 883w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 672px" /></p><p>有网民表示 30 元可以看 imax 电影，如果不需在门市排队就化算；另外有网民指已成功购买 imax 戏飞， 连同手续费则是 40 元。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229929" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/3-2-694x179.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="179" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/3-2-694x179.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/3-2.jpg 882w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229930" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/4-1-694x182.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="182" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/4-1-694x182.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/4-1.jpg 885w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>有人欢喜有人愁，有网民表示已经去到银行应用程式确认付款的阶段，但回到购票网页就只看见白画面，亦没有收到任何确认电邮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229931" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/5-1-675x580.jpg" alt="" width="675" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/5-1-675x580.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/5-1.jpg 868w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 675px" /></p><p>下面有网民回应表示自己亦遇到同样情况，银行显示已经收取相关费用，但就没有收到确认购票电邮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229932" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/6-694x517.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/6-694x517.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/6.jpg 872w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>有网民称，以往「买一送一」优惠，每张戏飞计算下来也只仅是 30 余元，无必要特地去抢，又指轮候时间过长，宁愿原价购买。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/7-694x179.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="179" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/7-694x179.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/7.jpg 878w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/9-694x151.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="151" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/9-694x151.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/9.jpg 881w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>另外亦有网民指，喜欢看电影的朋友应该不会购买这次戏院节的戏飞。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229934" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/8-694x249.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="249" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/8-694x249.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/8.jpg 878w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「全港戏院日」为「香港流行文化节 2024 」的一部份，当日不设长者、小童及学生优惠，而所有戏院优惠及电影赠券亦不适用。如长者首场优惠票价已低于 30 元，售价将维持不变。30 元的优惠票价同时适用于 IMAX、4DX 等戏票。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3676172">LIHKG</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/11/cinema-day/movie-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">4 月 21 日全港戏院日，票价划一 30 元</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/cinema-day-2024/movie-2/">全港戏院日开始售票，网民：「银行已扣钱但未收到确认电邮」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/cinema-day-2024/movie-2/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
