        </item>
        <item>
            <title>网民：蔚来 AI 令离婚率上升，能列举谁坐过副驾驶位</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/nio-car-raise-divorce-rate-said-chinese-twitter-user/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nio-car-raise-divorce-rate-said-chinese-twitter-user</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/nio-car-raise-divorce-rate-said-chinese-twitter-user/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:48:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NIO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[蔚来汽车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229879</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>人工智能日新月异，现在很多电动车也内置人工智能助手，能够智能调节车内温度、调校各种设定，甚至可以自动泊车，为驾驶者和乘客提供更方便的驾驶和乘坐体验。不过近日有中国网民就发现，中国蔚来电动车内置的「人工智能车载系统」除了上述功能外，更可以化身私家侦探，替用家「捉奸」。</p><p>X（前称 Twitter） 用户 @xiaojingcanxue 日前发文表：「蔚来人工智能能够大幅拉升离婚率」，并附上一条使用蔚来人工智能的影片。影片中可见拍摄人问蔚来人工智能本周有几多个人坐个副驾驶位置，蔚来人工智能诚实地回应指，这个星期坐在副驾驶的有拍摄者的朋友李先生、同事王女士及一位不认识的先生，甚至能够列举出这几位副驾驶座乘客甚么时候乘车，在车厢做了甚么。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229881" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcis7bgaaav5f-264x580.jpg" alt="" width="264" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcis7bgaaav5f-264x580.jpg 264w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcis7bgaaav5f-scaled.jpg 409w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 264px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/xiaojingcanxue/status/1779981255540633740">xiaojingcanxue@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229882" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcjp7a0aawdme-264x580.jpg" alt="" width="264" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcjp7a0aawdme-264x580.jpg 264w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcjp7a0aawdme-scaled.jpg 409w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 264px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/xiaojingcanxue/status/1779981255540633740">xiaojingcanxue@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpconiauaefak3-264x580.jpg" alt="" width="264" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpconiauaefak3-264x580.jpg 264w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpconiauaefak3-scaled.jpg 409w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 264px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/xiaojingcanxue/status/1779981255540633740">xiaojingcanxue@X</a></p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="zh" dir="ltr">离婚神器，蔚来人工智能车载系统视频演示。 <a href="https://t.co/Q9t1dbcmjR">pic.twitter.com/Q9t1dbcmjR</a></p><p>&mdash; 小径残雪 (@xiaojingcanxue) <a href="https://twitter.com/xiaojingcanxue/status/1779981255540633740?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 15, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>有网民回应指，这个发现不仅会令蔚来销量大跌，甚至会影响其他新款电动车的销量。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125604-694x251.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="251" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125604-694x251.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125604.jpg 742w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>有网民认为车内人工智能监视着一举一动，非常可怕。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229887" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125719-694x111.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="111" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125719-694x111.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125719.jpg 751w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/xiaojingcanxue/status/1779979963921547667">xiaojingcanxue@X</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/18/change-face-with-ai/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】Change Face With AI 换脸术，一键即换头</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/19/openai-gpt-store-2/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】GPT Store 正式开放 ChatGPT AI 女朋友 + 一张相帮你谂食谱</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/16/ai-hallucination/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">全球最大避险基金桥水用 AI 投资，或有机会出现「AI 幻觉」虚假资讯</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/nio-car-raise-divorce-rate-said-chinese-twitter-user/fun-tech/">网民：蔚来 AI 令离婚率上升，能列举谁坐过副驾驶位</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
